## 🧠 How KNN Works

The K-Nearest Neighbors algorithm works on the **proximity principle**: similar things exist in close proximity.
K=5. Majority Vote: BLUE

● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ●
● ● ● ● ● ? ● ● ● ● ●
● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ●
● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ●
● ● ● ● ● ● ● ● ●

● = Blue Class ● = Red Class ? = Unknown
The 5 nearest neighbors are all blue → Predict BLUE

